<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1437,1544,1823]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,561,1544,1571]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Record as epibiont on cnidarians:</emphasis>
This species was reported on hydroids from Strait of 
<collectingCountry box="[1180,1270,1544,1570]" name="Georgia" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Georgia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Wailes, G. H." box="[1286,1432,1544,1571]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" refId="ref18764" refString="Wailes, G. H. (1943) Canadian Pacific fauna. 1. Protozoa. 1 f. Ciliata. 1 g. Suctoria. University of Toronto Press, Toronro, 46 pp." type="book" year="1943">Wailes 1943</bibRefCitation>
: 
<bibRefCitation author="Mccazuley, J. E. &amp; Hancock, D. R." box="[151,476,1580,1607]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" pagination="8" refId="ref16355" refString="Mccazuley, J. E. &amp; Hancock, D. R. (1971) Appendix 8. Annotated checklist of plants and animals. In: Oceanography of the Nearshore Coastal Waters of the Pacific Northwest. Vol. 2. Oregon State University, Corvallis, Oregon, pp. 165 - 744." type="book chapter" year="1971">Mccazuley &amp; Hancock 1971</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="169" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="18.[151,1437,1544,1823]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,735,1616,1643]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Record as epibiont on other hosts/ substrata:</emphasis>
This species was found also on Bryozoa and algae from Strait of Georgia (
<bibRefCitation author="Wailes, G. H." box="[284,427,1652,1679]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" refId="ref18764" refString="Wailes, G. H. (1943) Canadian Pacific fauna. 1. Protozoa. 1 f. Ciliata. 1 g. Suctoria. University of Toronto Press, Toronro, 46 pp." type="book" year="1943">Wailes 1943</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Mccazuley, J. E. &amp; Hancock, D. R." box="[437,760,1652,1679]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" pagination="8" refId="ref16355" refString="Mccazuley, J. E. &amp; Hancock, D. R. (1971) Appendix 8. Annotated checklist of plants and animals. In: Oceanography of the Nearshore Coastal Waters of the Pacific Northwest. Vol. 2. Oregon State University, Corvallis, Oregon, pp. 165 - 744." type="book chapter" year="1971">Mccazuley &amp; Hancock 1971</bibRefCitation>
). Widely distributed marine species, found on different hosts and substrates in the caribbean mangrove peat wall sunken wood and leaf debris in Twin CaysIsland, 
<collectingCountry box="[1316,1388,1688,1714]" name="Belize" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Belize</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingRegion box="[151,289,1724,1750]" country="France" name="Guadeloupe" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Guadeloupe</collectingRegion>
, French West Indies; in the Gulf of Mexico, in the Florida Keys; in the Atlantic Ocean, Lanzarote, the Canary Islands; on rocks near sea grass debris accumulation in the Mediterranean Sea, 
<collectingCountry box="[1130,1218,1760,1786]" name="France" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Corsica</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1229,1309,1761,1787]" name="France" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">France</collectingCountry>
; in the Red Sea and growing on bones of a whale fall deployed in the 
<collectingRegion box="[801,872,1796,1822]" country="Japan" name="Tokyo" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Tokyo</collectingRegion>
Bay, 
<collectingCountry box="[936,1000,1797,1823]" name="Japan" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">Japan</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Bright, M. &amp; Espada-Hinojosa, S. &amp; Lagkouvardos, I. &amp; Volland, J. M." box="[1014,1219,1796,1823]" pageId="18" pageNumber="169" pagination="1 - 13" refId="ref12469" refString="Bright, M., Espada-Hinojosa, S., Lagkouvardos, I. &amp; Volland, J. M. (2014) The giant ciliate Zoothanmium niveum and its thiotrophic epibiont Candidatus Thiobios zoothamnicoli: a model system to study interspecies cooperation. Frontiers in Microbiology, 5 (145), 1 - 13. https: // doi. org / 10.3389 / fmicb. 2014.00145" type="journal article" year="2014">
Bright 
<emphasis box="[1095,1144,1796,1822]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="169">et al</emphasis>
. 2014
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
